title: Coffin Fuck - Death Metal Christmas Covers(2006,2007,2008)
description:
Comedy-Death Metal Christmas covers from 2006, 2007, and 2008 for those who have a sense of humor.

The songs are totally clean, fun for the whole family.

If you enjoy, please spread the word!

Track listing:
2006: Deck the Halls
2007: Grandma Got Ran Over by a Reindeer
2008: Medley of great hits(and something at the end for the jewish)
